<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id78438b0c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1990—<ref href="/us/pl/101/512">Pub. L. 101–512</ref> substituted “$100,000” for “$35,000”.</p>
